text: Is there anyway we can request an API log from HubSpot on a portal?
One of customers keeps hitting their limit and they are trying to see which api is causing this to happen

As an FYI, I asked support about an API log and they mentioned its not available publicly facing at this time. When asked if they could provide the export for me since it wasn't public facing I was redirected to the HubSpot Developer Forums to try and get an answer and was told if it was possible someone there would respond on it
If I could get any kind of export with IP addresses so we can get that info of where its coming from precisely, that would be awesome.
